title: Tim Pool & Keemstar Dark Alliance, Beans On Toast - Off The Rails #33
description: Today we have AB's boxing coach, Lucky Boy, to share his incredible story of moving from Nigeria to pursue boxing around the globe. We also discuss the cursed team-up of Tim Pool/Keemstar, an update to the beans on toast debate with a vegemite twist, an unexpected return of the Fika Fish, & much more!
